law.history: Repealed 1944 (2d Extra Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1, Part Four, 3. -- Repealed 1944 Ky. Acts ch. 154, sec. 29. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2554e-11.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Appropriation to Department of Revenue for enforcement of laws relating to alcoholic beverages.
